{"type":"message","id":"a5d5bb36","parentId":"8c3bc3fd","timestamp":"2026-03-09T06:38:42.313Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户提供了一个 tushare 文档链接，需要读取该链接获取实时数据接口的相关信息。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_58701c1c2b5d4c409c9ddc1b","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/skills/tushare-data/references/股票数据/行情数据/实时日线.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-35b-a3b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773038320461}}
{"type":"message","id":"7f548cda","parentId":"a5d5bb36","timestamp":"2026-03-09T06:38:42.318Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_58701c1c2b5d4c409c9ddc1b","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 沪深京实时日线\n----\n\n接口：rt_k\n描述：获取实时日k线行情，支持按股票代码及股票代码通配符一次性提取全部股票实时日k线行情\n限量：单次最大可提取6000条数据，等同于一次提取全市场\n积分：本接口是单独开权限的数据，单独申请权限请参考[权限列表](https://tushare.pro/document/1?doc_id=290)，可以[在线开通](https://tushare.pro/weborder/#/permission)权限。\n\n<br>\n<br>\n\n**输入参数**\n\n名称 | 类型  | 必选 | 描述\n---- | ----- | ---- | ----\nts_code | str | Y | 支持通配符方式，e.g. 所有上交所股票：6\\*.SH、所有创业板股票3\\*.SZ、所有科创板股票688*.SH，或单个股票600000.SH\n\n<br>\n注：ts_code代码一定要带<font color=\"red\">.SH/.SZ/.BJ</font>后缀\n\n\n<br>\n\n\n**输出参数**\n\n名称 | 类型 | 默认显示 | 描述\n--- | ---- | ---- | ----\nts_code | str | Y | 股票代码\nname | None | Y | 股票名称\npre_close | float | Y | 昨收价\nhigh | float | Y | 最高价\nopen | float | Y | 开盘价\nlow | float | Y | 最低价\nclose | float | Y | 收盘价（最新价）\nvol | int | Y | 成交量（股）\namount | int | Y | 成交金额（元）\nnum | int | Y | 开盘以来成交笔数\nask_price1 | float | N | 委托卖盘（元）\nask_volume1 | int | N | 委托卖盘（股）\nbid_price1 | float | N | 委托买盘（元）\nbid_volume1 | int | N | 委托买盘（股）\ntrade_time | str | N | 交易时间\n\n<br>\n<br>\n\n**接口示例**\n\n```python\n\n#获取今日开盘以来所有创业板实时日线和成交笔数\ndf = pro.rt_k(ts_code='3*.SZ')\n\n#获取今日开盘以来全市场所有股票实时日线和成交笔数（不建议一次提取全市场，可分批提取性能更好）\ndf = pro.rt_k(ts_code='3*.SZ,6*.SH,0*.SZ,9*.BJ')\n\n#获取当日开盘以来单个股票实时日线和成交笔数\ndf = pro.rt_k(ts_code='600000.SH,000001.SZ')\n\n```\n\n\n<br>\n<br>\n\n**数据示例**\n\n\t\t\tts_code  name      pre_close   high   open   low  close     vol      amount     num\n\t0    601866.SH  中远海发       2.28   2.28   2.28   2.23   2.24  55845293  125364882  19904\n\t1    601811.SH  新华文轩      15.47  15.59  15.42  15.24  15.46   4169900   64212329  10524\n\t2    601877.SH  正泰电器      22.06  22.10  22.06  21.81  21.89   9816735  215350906  21733\n\t3    601699.SH  潞安环能      11.78  11.77  11.77  11.56  11.61  12121234  140750449  13836\n\t4    601858.SH  中国科传      18.45  18.77  18.56  18.36  18.56   2665300   49383660   7033\n\t..         ...   ...        ...    ...    ...    ...    ...         ...          ...      ...\n\t220  601880.SH  辽港股份       1.50   1.50   1.50   1.46   1.47  79855960  117767408  11820\n\t221  601616.SH  广电电气       4.00   4.05   4.02   3.96   4.03  18984200   75975252  18220\n\t222  601611.SH  中国核建       8.86   8.86   8.86   8.62   8.67  27793715  241360488  24970\n\t223  601218.SH  吉鑫科技       3.00   3.02   2.99   2.96   3.00  10487500   31316964   6327\n\t224  601966.SH  玲珑轮胎      15.31  15.38  15.38  15.18  15.27  11297200  172527086  31828"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773038322316}}
{"type":"message","id":"e54d8f77","parentId":"7f548cda","timestamp":"2026-03-09T06:38:51.118Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"已读取文档了解了 tushare 的实时日线接口 rt_k，现在需要用该接口获取中国石油的实时行情数据。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"📊 **tushare 实时行情接口说明**\n\n根据官方文档，tushare 提供 **实时日线行情 (rt_k)** 接口：\n\n---\n\n**✅ 如何获取实时数据：**\n\n```python\nimport tushare as ts\nimport os\n\ntoken = os.getenv('TUSHARE_TOKEN')\npro = ts.pro_api(token)\n\n# 方式 1: 查询单个股票实时行情\ndf = pro.rt_k(ts_code='601857.SH')\nprint(df)\n\n# 方式 2: 批量查询（支持通配符）\ndf = pro.rt_k(ts_code='3*.SZ,6*.SH,0*.SZ,9*.BJ')\n\n# 返回字段包括：\n# - close: 最新价\n# - open/high/low/pre_close: 开盘/最高/最低/昨收\n# - vol/amount: 成交量/成交额\n# - bid_price1/ask_price1: 买卖盘口\n# - trade_time: 交易时间\n```\n\n---\n\n**⚠️ 注意事项：**\n- 该接口需要**单独申请权限**（积分要求）\n- 非交易时段可能不返回数据\n- 需要在交易日 9:30-15:00 之间调用\n\n---\n\n让我帮您测试一下这个接口能否使用：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_acaa5d6cbf704146a023ea57","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'EOF'\nimport os\nimport tushare as ts\nimport pandas as pd\n\ntoken = os.getenv('TUSHARE_TOKEN')\npro = ts.pro_api(token)\n\ntry:\n    # 尝试获取实时日线\n    df = pro.rt_k(ts_code='601857.SH')\n    \n    if len(df) > 0:\n        print(\"=\" * 70)\n        print(\"📊 中国石油 (601857.SH) - 实时行情\")\n        print(\"=\" * 70)\n        row = df.iloc[0]\n        print(f\"🕐 交易时间：{row.get('trade_time', 'N/A')}\")\n        print(f\"💰 最新价：{row['close']:.2f}\")\n        print(f\"↗️ 涨跌额：{row['close'] - row['pre_close']:.2f}\")\n        print(f\"📈 涨跌幅：{(row['close'] - row['pre_close']) / row['pre_close'] * 100:.2f}%\")\n        print(f\"🔼 今开：{row['open']:.2f}\")\n        print(f\"🔺 最高：{row['high']:.2f}\")\n        print(f\"🔻 最低：{row['low']:.2f}\")\n        print(f\"⚖️ 昨收：{row['pre_close']:.2f}\")\n        print(f\"📊 成交量：{row['vol']/10000:.2f} 万手\")\n        print(f\"💵 成交额：{row['amount']/10000:.2f} 万元\")\n        \n        # 如果有买一卖一\n        if 'bid_price1' in df.columns and row['bid_price1']:\n            print(f\"\\n📋 五档盘口:\")\n            print(f\"   卖一：{row['ask_price1']:.2f} ({row['ask_volume1']/10000:.2f}万手)\")\n            print(f\"   买一：{row['bid_price1']:.2f} ({row['bid_volume1']/10000:.2f}万手)\")\n            \n        print(\"=\" * 70)\n        print(\"数据来源：tushare.pro (实时日线接口)\")\n    else:\n        print(\"未获取到实时数据 - 可能是非交易时段或权限不足\")\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"调用失败：{e}\")\nEOF\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-35b-a3b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773038322319}}
