{"type":"message","id":"d37fcf3f","parentId":"88c8df2f","timestamp":"2026-03-09T06:39:48.452Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"rt_k 接口有每分钟仅 1 次的调用限制，无法批量查询所有股票，需要向用户说明这个情况并提供替代方案。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"⚠️ **rt_k 实时接口有调用限制**\n\ntushare pro 的实时日线接口 (**rt_k**) 权限：**每分钟最多 1 次访问**\n\n这意味着：\n- ❌ 无法批量查询多只股票\n- ✅ 可以逐个查询（需要等 1 分钟冷却）\n\n---\n\n**💡 建议方案：**\n\n1. **使用 tushare 日 K 线 (daily)** - 收盘数据，无限次查询\n   ```python\n   pro.daily(ts_code='601857.SH', start_date='20260306')\n   ```\n\n2. **直接访问财经网站** - 盘中实时行情\n   - 东方财富：https://quote.eastmoney.com/sz601857.html\n   - 同花顺：https://www.10jqka.com.cn/stock/601857.html\n\n3. **分批查询** - 每次间隔 1 分钟以上\n\n---\n\n您想：\n- 🔹 用 daily 接口查看最新收盘数据？\n- 🔹 逐个手动查询某几只股票的实时行情？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-35b-a3b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773038385246}}
